07:43.830 --> 07:46.060
And Rita.

07:46.130 --> 07:47.490
Ah, wait,
wait a second.

07:47.560 --> 07:51.270
Uh, Cecilia, Dorothy...

07:51.330 --> 07:54.670
And this is Kenneth,

07:54.740 --> 07:58.410
and...Bambi.

07:58.470 --> 08:00.970
This is my son Sigmund and my wife Fay

08:01.040 --> 08:04.110
