and that's my sister Lily.

08:04.180 --> 08:07.080
Lily?
I was close.

08:07.150 --> 08:08.850
It's a beautiful family.

08:08.920 --> 08:10.880
Thanyou.

08:10.950 --> 08:12.890
Have a seat.

08:28.340 --> 08:31.940
Why don't I start, huh?

