08:36.210 --> 08:40.250
I have problems.

08:40.320 --> 08:43.080
Uh, I worry about diseases,

08:43.150 --> 08:46.420
so I have trouble touching things.

08:46.490 --> 08:51.730
Uh, in public places
it's almost impossible.

08:51.790 --> 08:55.030
I have a real big problem moving.

08:55.100 --> 08:57.700
Talk about...Moving.

09:00.640 --> 09:03.600
As long as I'm in my apartment I'm okay.

09:03.670 --> 09:07.340
But when I want to go out,
I get...

09:07.410 --> 09:10.080
Weird.

09:10.150 --> 09:11.810
Talk about weird.

09:11.880 --> 09:13.380
Talk about weird.

09:13.450 --> 09:18.020
Well, I get dizzy spells.

09:18.090 --> 09:22.960
Nausea, cold sweats...

09:23.020 --> 09:24.430
Hot sweats,

09:24.490 --> 09:26.690
fever blisters,
difficulty breathing,

09:26.760 --> 09:29.160
difficulty swallowing,

09:29.230 --> 09:33.730
blurred vision,
involuntary trembling, dead hands,

09:33.800 --> 09:38.810
numb lips,
fingernail sensitivity,

09:38.870 --> 09:41.810
pelvic discomfort.

09:41.880 --> 09:45.880
So the real question is,
what is the crisis, Bob?

09:45.950 --> 09:50.280
What is it that you are truly afraid of?

09:50.350 --> 09:52.990
What if my heart stops beating?

09:53.050 --> 09:55.420
What if I'm looking for a bathroom?

09:55.490 --> 09:59.690
I can't find it... and...

09:59.760 --> 10:02.930
My bladder explodes.

10:03.000 --> 10:05.200
Have you ever heard of
tourette's syndrome?

10:05.270 --> 10:06.700
Mm-hmm.

10:06.770 --> 10:10.000
Involuntarily shouting profanity.

10:10.070 --> 10:11.840
It's exceptionally rare.

10:11.910 --> 10:15.080
Shit-eating son of a bitch!

10:15.140 --> 10:17.910
Bastard, douchebag, twat!

10:17.980 --> 10:21.550
Numb-nuts, dickhead, bitch!

10:21.620 --> 10:24.920
Why, exactly,
are you doing this?

10:24.990 --> 10:29.990
If I fake it,
then I don't have it.

10:30.060 --> 10:32.130
You know,
it's the same with the cardiac arrest.

10:32.190 --> 10:34.700
[Grunts and gasps]

10:44.040 --> 10:46.040
Are you married?

10:46.110 --> 10:48.640
I'm divorced.

10:48.710 --> 10:51.450
Would you like to talk about that?

10:51.510 --> 10:54.080
There are two types of
people in this world.

10:54.150 --> 10:57.220
Those who like Neil diamond
and those who don't.

10:57.290 --> 11:01.320
My ex-wife loves him.

11:01.390 --> 11:03.060
I see.

11:03.120 --> 11:04.890
So what you're saying
is that even though

11:04.960 --> 11:08.060
you are an almost paralyzed,

11:08.130 --> 11:09.630
multi-phobic personality

11:09.700 --> 11:12.000
that is in a constant state of panic,

11:12.070 --> 11:14.500
your wife did not leave you,
you left her

11:14.570 --> 11:19.170
because she liked Neil diamond?

11:19.240 --> 11:22.580
Now, you're saying that maybe--

11:22.640 --> 11:25.350
maybe I didn't leave her
because she likes Neil diamond,

11:25.410 --> 11:28.250
but maybe-- maybe she left me?

11:28.320 --> 11:30.120
Yes.

11:30.190 --> 11:32.420
Ow!
Ow!

11:32.490 --> 11:34.960
Ow!
Ow!

11:35.020 --> 11:37.520
Ow!

11:41.060 --> 11:46.300
Dr. Marvin...
you can help me.

11:46.370 --> 11:49.140
For the first time in my
life I feel like there's hope.

11:52.570 --> 11:54.810
I feel like I can be somebody.

11:57.510 --> 12:01.650
Bob, there's an old saying...

12:01.720 --> 12:04.850
That the best psychiatrist in the world...

12:04.920 --> 12:06.920
Is the one right inside of you.

12:06.990 --> 12:08.460
Yeah.

12:08.520 --> 12:10.890
I can help you, yes.

12:10.960 --> 12:14.160
Thank you.

12:14.230 --> 12:17.300
Bob, there is a groundbreaking new book

12:17.370 --> 12:19.130
that has just come out.

12:19.200 --> 12:22.170
Ah!

12:22.240 --> 12:24.300
Now, not everything in this book,

12:24.370 --> 12:25.640
of course,
applies to you,

12:25.710 --> 12:27.240
but I'm sure that you can see,

12:27.310 --> 12:30.180
when you see the title,

12:30.250 --> 12:33.350
exactly how it could help.

12:33.420 --> 12:35.250
Baby steps?

12:35.320 --> 12:39.850
It means setting small,
reasonable goals for yourself

12:39.920 --> 12:44.490
one day at a time,
one tiny step at a time.

12:44.560 --> 12:48.030
Baby steps.

