For instance, um,
when you leave this office,

12:51.400 --> 12:53.170
don't think about
everything you have to do

12:53.230 --> 12:56.100
in order to get out of the building.

12:56.170 --> 12:59.470
Just think of what you must
do to get out of this room.

12:59.540 --> 13:01.310
And when you get to the hall,

13:01.380 --> 13:04.550
deal with that hall and so forth.

13:04.610 --> 13:07.380
You see?

13:07.450 --> 13:09.450
- Baby steps!
- Baby steps.

13:09.520 --> 13:11.420
Oh, boy.

13:11.490 --> 13:16.690
Baby steps.
Baby steps.

