Baby steps through the office?

13:19.460 --> 13:22.730
Baby steps out the door.

13:25.230 --> 13:27.230
It worked.

13:27.300 --> 13:29.200
It works.

13:32.340 --> 13:33.940
All I have to do

13:34.010 --> 13:37.240
