while I'm on vacation.

13:47.390 --> 13:52.360
Va--vacation?

13:52.430 --> 13:55.260
Oh, certainly my secretary told you.

13:55.330 --> 13:57.030
As of this afternoon,
I'm taking my family

13:57.100 --> 13:58.500
on vacation until labor day.

14:01.400 --> 14:04.240
That's a month.

14:04.310 --> 14:07.040
What if I need you?
What if I need to talk?

14:07.110 --> 14:08.340
Well, my associate,
Dr. harmon,

14:08.410 --> 14:09.640
would be happy to talk.

14:09.710 --> 14:12.680
And, Bob,
I'll be back.

14:12.750 --> 14:14.750
<i>Just read baby steps.</i>

14:14.820 --> 14:17.420
Baby steps out of the office.

14:17.490 --> 14:19.620
Very good.

14:19.690 --> 14:22.190
Baby steps to the hall.

14:22.260 --> 14:24.660
Very good, Bob.
Keep going.

14:24.730 --> 14:27.630
That's it.
Bye.

14:27.700 --> 14:28.700
I'll see you in a month.

