16:10.230 --> 16:13.570
Bob, I can't give out that number.

16:13.640 --> 16:15.770
I know that, Betty,
but you could

16:15.840 --> 16:17.500
call him on the other line

16:17.570 --> 16:19.670
and tell him that I'm on
hold on the other line.

16:19.740 --> 16:22.610
Couldn't you, please?
Thanks, Betty, please?

16:25.880 --> 16:27.780
Siggy, honey,
put that down in front

16:27.850 --> 16:29.780
