put him through.

17:05.520 --> 17:07.520
Go ahead, Bob.

17:07.589 --> 17:08.589
This is Dr. Marvin.

17:08.660 --> 17:10.760
What's the problem, Bob?

17:10.829 --> 17:13.430
Dr. Marvin,
how's the weather up there?

17:13.500 --> 17:15.359
What?

17:15.430 --> 17:16.660
How's your brood?

17:16.730 --> 17:19.300
You all getting a chance to relax?

17:19.369 --> 17:21.800
Bob, I thought I made it clear

17:21.869 --> 17:24.810
