17:24.869 --> 17:26.569
Well, I know,
but I'm just worse than usual this time.

17:26.640 --> 17:28.210
Really bad.

17:28.280 --> 17:29.640
Bob, if this is really an emergency,

17:29.710 --> 17:31.780
go to the emergency room.

17:31.850 --> 17:32.780
And if it isn't,
call Dr. harmon.

17:32.850 --> 17:34.450
I'm sure he can help you.

17:34.520 --> 17:36.220
Well, I'd just feel so much better

17:36.280 --> 17:37.790
if I knew where you were.

17:37.850 --> 17:39.250
It's Martha's vineyard, right?

17:39.320 --> 17:40.690
Bob.

17:40.760 --> 17:41.720
Well, can't we just talk?

17:41.790 --> 17:42.890
Yes, we can.

17:42.960 --> 17:45.260
In my office after labor day.

17:45.330 --> 17:46.760
After you're back from fire island, huh?

17:46.830 --> 17:48.930
Good-bye, Bob.

17:49.000 --> 17:50.830
What, you want to keep
Maine all to yourself?

17:50.900 --> 17:54.800
Good-bye, Bob!

17:54.870 --> 17:58.540
Is this a fake hang up?

17:58.610 --> 18:01.180
It's a fake hang up.

18:01.240 --> 18:02.440
- Eat these beans.
- No, no.

18:02.510 --> 18:04.140
[Phone ringing]

18:04.210 --> 18:06.750
I'll get the phone.
I'll get the phone.

18:12.350 --> 18:13.750
