18:13.820 --> 18:15.190
Doctor, it's Betty again.

18:15.260 --> 18:17.660
I have an urgent call from your sister.

18:17.730 --> 18:20.190
My sister?
Put her through.

18:20.260 --> 18:21.330
Go ahead.

18:26.330 --> 18:30.770
It's not you,
it's me.

18:30.840 --> 18:33.470
Lily, what's wrong?

18:33.540 --> 18:34.780
Dr. Marvin,
please don't be angry.

18:34.840 --> 18:36.740
This is Bob.

18:36.810 --> 18:38.480
I know that I shouldn't
be calling you here--

18:38.550 --> 18:40.980
Bob, the doctor/patient
relationship is based on trust.

18:41.050 --> 18:42.720
When you call me and
pretend to be my sister,

18:42.780 --> 18:44.080
I can't trust you anymore.

18:44.150 --> 18:45.620
Go to the emergency room,
but please

18:45.690 --> 18:49.620
