19:01.840 --> 19:03.670
Who is it?

19:03.740 --> 19:05.140
Detective Roberts from homicide.

19:05.210 --> 19:08.280
I have some questions
about a Bob Wiley.

19:08.340 --> 19:10.010
What?

19:10.080 --> 19:15.080
That was the Bob who
kept calling Dr. Marvin.

19:15.150 --> 19:19.490
That was that Bob who kept calling.

19:19.550 --> 19:23.220
Unfortunately, Bob committed
suicide about 15 minutes ago.

19:23.290 --> 19:25.330
Oh, my God.

19:25.390 --> 19:26.860
- That's terrible.
- Oh.

19:26.930 --> 19:28.230
Very sad.

19:28.300 --> 19:29.460
Should never have happened.

19:29.530 --> 19:31.330
He was a very sweet guy.

19:31.400 --> 19:32.830
But he did leave a note, however.

19:32.900 --> 19:33.970
He mentioned the name Betty.

19:34.040 --> 19:35.870
- She's Betty.
- I'm Betty.

19:35.940 --> 19:39.910
Oh, so you're Betty.

19:39.970 --> 19:43.010
