- Dad!

52:40.020 --> 52:40.950
Honey?

52:41.020 --> 52:43.390
Dad!

52:43.460 --> 52:48.660
Don't panic.
I know what to do.

52:48.730 --> 52:52.430
Don't worry.
I got it.

52:52.500 --> 52:55.340
Okay?

52:55.400 --> 52:56.700
Oh, my God!

52:56.770 --> 52:59.010
[Overlapping yelling]

52:59.070 --> 53:01.680
I'm doing the right thing.

53:01.740 --> 53:02.880
He's still choking!

53:02.940 --> 53:05.110
- He's turning blue!
- Now?

53:05.180 --> 53:07.610
There's one other thing I can do.

53:07.680 --> 53:10.620
[Overlapping yelling]

53:10.690 --> 53:12.590
Honey, I love you!
Breathe!

53:12.650 --> 53:14.050
Harder!
Maybe with your knee more.

53:14.120 --> 53:16.490
Hit him harder!
Jump higher.

53:16.560 --> 53:18.330
- Oh!
- Spit it out!

53:18.390 --> 53:21.630
- He's still blue!
- He's still blue!

53:21.700 --> 53:24.530
- Ah!
- Spit again! Breathe!

53:24.600 --> 53:26.970
- [Gags and exhales]
- Leo, are you okay?

53:27.040 --> 53:28.370
Get him off me.

53:28.440 --> 53:32.410
Get him off me!

53:32.470 --> 53:34.410
Dad.

53:34.480 --> 53:36.780
Bob, you saved him!

53:36.850 --> 53:39.980
That was incredible.

53:40.050 --> 53:44.550
I just never gave up hope.

53:44.620 --> 53:45.690
[Thunder]

53:45.750 --> 53:47.890
Aah!
Oh!

53:47.960 --> 53:49.790
Shh, it's all right.
It's okay.

53:49.860 --> 53:54.800
