54:27.060 --> 54:29.030
♪ I'm singin' in the rain ♪

54:29.100 --> 54:32.470
♪ singin' in the rain ♪

54:32.530 --> 54:33.800
I don't like being a party poop,

54:33.870 --> 54:35.870
but tomorrow's very important

54:35.940 --> 54:38.770
and I think we better call it a night.

54:38.840 --> 54:42.310
[Singing continues]

54:42.380 --> 54:43.980
I don't wanna be rude,

54:44.050 --> 54:46.550
